including hat pins.

30:11.309 --> 30:13.344
How could they have known
that he gave me a hat pin?

30:13.477 --> 30:16.280
Frank Carter is a great lawyer.

30:16.414 --> 30:17.748
I'll introduce you.

30:17.848 --> 30:20.518
He'll help you
with the affidavit.

30:20.651 --> 30:22.753
Can you please
tell the president about this?

30:22.853 --> 30:25.656
