35:01.899 --> 35:03.767
All right, all right, look,

35:03.901 --> 35:05.135
here's what we're gonna do,
okay?

35:05.269 --> 35:06.604
I-I'm gonna call Bob Bennett.

35:06.770 --> 35:08.105
Ugh. (laughs airily)

35:08.239 --> 35:10.274
I know you're not a fan,
but he's a reasonable guy.

35:10.408 --> 35:11.775
-Oh, yeah.
-I'm gonna tell him about this,

35:11.909 --> 35:14.278
and push him to settle now
with Paula Jones.

35:14.445 --> 35:16.580
