every gift you've ever given me,

37:42.526 --> 37:43.761
and it just feels too dangerous.

37:43.927 --> 37:45.195
Well, d-don't worry about that.

37:45.295 --> 37:46.930
I am worried.

37:47.064 --> 37:49.367
Don't you think that
something weird is going on?

37:49.467 --> 37:52.570
I wish I did.
I'm sorry you're having

37:52.703 --> 37:55.939
