this is what they do to me

37:56.106 --> 37:58.275
and anyone I'm close to.

37:58.442 --> 38:02.079
You know, sad thing is,
just feels normal to me now.

38:02.212 --> 38:05.148
Okay. I just... I guess
it feels different for me.

38:05.282 --> 38:07.451
I don't know.
