41:39.863 --> 41:42.265
Paula Jones' lawyers
behind the scenes.

41:46.837 --> 41:48.706
I see you two are very excited.

41:48.839 --> 41:51.541
But I need to figure out

41:51.675 --> 41:54.011
how I can justify this
under our mandate.

41:54.144 --> 41:56.113
(laughing):
What? What?

41:56.213 --> 41:57.615
Vernon Jordan's
the president's fixer.

41:57.715 --> 41:59.016
How many
of our Whitewater witnesses

41:59.182 --> 42:00.851
-has he interfered with?
-Allegedly.

42:00.984 --> 42:02.285
Let's just see
if it's real, Judge.

42:02.385 --> 42:04.855
We'll go
where the evidence leads.

42:07.991 --> 42:09.860
Look into it,
but remember who we are.

42:09.993 --> 42:12.830
This is a federal investigation
reporting directly

42:12.963 --> 42:15.065
to the United States Congress.

42:15.198 --> 42:17.067
No more of this backdoor stuff
with your friends.

42:17.200 --> 42:19.069
It has to appear
that this witness came

42:19.202 --> 42:20.537
to us out of the blue.

42:20.671 --> 42:22.005
She has to call us.

42:22.139 --> 42:23.874
We... Yeah, got it.
Go, go, go.

42:25.342 --> 42:26.977
(door closes)

42:27.978 --> 42:29.512
