you'd all come briefed.

45:00.630 --> 45:03.366
Well, please sit.

45:03.500 --> 45:07.871
Uh, in short, I've been
subpoenaed in the Jones suit,

45:08.005 --> 45:12.642
and I'm being pressured
into a... a cover-up

45:12.742 --> 45:16.046
at the direction of the
president of the United States.

45:16.213 --> 45:19.049
Just to confirm-- this involves
your colleague Monica...

45:19.182 --> 45:22.052
Lewinsky.
A friend.

45:22.185 --> 45:24.221
A good friend.

45:25.222 --> 45:28.058
It's not simply my word on this.

45:28.191 --> 45:32.395
I-I have Monica
describing it all on tape.

45:34.264 --> 45:36.666
She also discusses
her sexual affair

45:36.766 --> 45:39.536
with the president...
in detail.

45:39.669 --> 45:43.540
So you started taping
when you got the subpoena?

45:43.673 --> 45:45.375
No.

45:45.508 --> 45:47.945
I began when I was subjected
to character assassination

45:48.078 --> 45:50.113
by the president's attorney
in Newsweek.

45:51.248 --> 45:53.083
I knew I had to protect myself.

45:53.216 --> 45:55.585
-From Bob Bennett.
-From the Clintons.

45:55.752 --> 45:58.288
We all know
what they're capable of.

45:58.421 --> 46:00.390
This Monica has no idea?

46:00.523 --> 46:01.758
Of course not.

46:01.925 --> 46:03.626
And I-I'm sorry.

46:03.760 --> 46:06.096
You referred to this person
as your "good friend"?

46:06.263 --> 46:07.430
What's that supposed to mean?

46:07.597 --> 46:09.599
Well, I'm just trying
to ascertain...

46:09.732 --> 46:12.469
Well, I have been Monica's sole
support for-for over a year.

46:12.602 --> 46:15.105
I've given her my time,
my-my counsel

46:15.272 --> 46:17.607
in her darkest, loneliest hour.

46:17.740 --> 46:19.709
There was one person she knew
would pick up the phone,

46:19.809 --> 46:21.711
and that was me.

46:21.811 --> 46:25.949
All I want,
all I have ever wanted

46:26.083 --> 46:30.120
is for Monica to be okay.

46:30.253 --> 46:32.289
But I had to protect myself.

46:33.723 --> 46:35.725
And thank fucking God I did.

46:35.825 --> 46:38.261
Mrs. Tripp,
we have been investigating

46:38.395 --> 46:40.130
the Clintons for years now.

46:40.297 --> 46:41.899
Yes, we know
what they're capable of,

46:41.999 --> 46:45.435
and we fully understand
why you did what you did, okay?

46:46.569 --> 46:49.139
Now, out of nowhere,
I learn it's illegal

46:49.306 --> 46:50.807
in Maryland to record a call.

46:50.974 --> 46:52.509
-I-I got horrible advice
on that.
-Yeah.

46:52.642 --> 46:55.946
We will help you avoid
prosecution, anything you need.

46:56.079 --> 46:58.481
We just need copies
of your tapes.

47:03.921 --> 47:05.655
I can have those
to you tomorrow.

47:08.658 --> 47:10.527
Okay, great.

47:10.660 --> 47:13.964
I'll have a clean tape
for you tomorrow, too.

47:14.097 --> 47:15.933
What do you mean,
"clean tape"?

47:16.033 --> 47:18.001
I've arranged lunch with Monica

47:18.135 --> 47:20.003
tomorrow in Virginia
where they're less dictatorial

47:20.137 --> 47:21.771
about single-party taping.

47:21.871 --> 47:24.107
I'm going to tape the whole
thing, but legal this time.

47:24.207 --> 47:26.043
-And how are you gonna do that?
-I'm going to wire myself

47:26.176 --> 47:28.345
with a recording device.
I plan to wear a loose blouse.

47:28.511 --> 47:31.014
No, no, no.
No, no way.

47:31.148 --> 47:32.782
This is an active
federal investigation.

47:32.882 --> 47:35.285
If you're gonna be wired, you're
gonna be wired by the FBI.

47:39.389 --> 47:41.191
You realize what this means?

47:41.324 --> 47:44.194
Clinton gives his deposition
in the Jones case on Saturday.

47:44.361 --> 47:47.197
He's gonna walk in there,
he's gonna lie his ass off.

47:47.364 --> 47:48.865
We're gonna be waiting for him.

47:48.999 --> 47:52.202
I mean, this is...
this is bigger than Whitewater.

47:52.335 --> 47:54.371
What? Fuck that.
It's bigger than Watergate, man.

47:54.504 --> 47:56.706
-We have tapes.
-Watergate had tapes.

47:56.873 --> 47:58.908
And thank God we do, too,

47:59.042 --> 48:02.179
'cause a jury would
fucking hate that lady.

48:10.720 --> 48:12.189
Just need to secure this.

48:12.322 --> 48:14.091
How is this different
than the one on my leg?

48:14.224 --> 48:15.892
This one lets us listen live
from up here.

48:16.026 --> 48:19.562
Linda, look, just-just focus
on two things, okay?

48:19.729 --> 48:21.931
She needs to say she's planning
on lying under oath

48:22.065 --> 48:24.001
and she needs to say what
Vernon Jordan is doing for her

48:24.101 --> 48:25.735
in exchange for that lie.

48:25.902 --> 48:27.737
-That's it.
-AGENT: Okay.

48:27.870 --> 48:28.905
Ms. Tripp,
can you say a few words?

48:29.039 --> 48:30.407
What if something goes wrong?

48:30.540 --> 48:31.574
We'll be listening in
the whole time,

48:31.708 --> 48:32.742
and we have people posted
downstairs.

48:32.875 --> 48:34.111
What if she sees them?

48:34.244 --> 48:36.413
-She won't.
-(scoffs)

48:38.681 --> 48:40.750
Why don't you go for a table
in the back corner?

48:40.917 --> 48:42.252
You'll be able
to see the whole place.

48:42.419 --> 48:44.187
It'll help you stay calm.

48:47.924 --> 48:49.959
I hope I don't let you down.

49:08.978 --> 49:10.447
-Hi.
-Hi.

49:10.613 --> 49:13.150
Uh, uh...

49:13.283 --> 49:15.585
I'd like that table
in the corner.

49:15.718 --> 49:17.620
-Oh, okay.
-It'll just be two of us.

49:17.787 --> 49:19.156
Sure. Wherever you like.

49:19.289 --> 49:22.292
Tell me
about your smoking policy.

49:22.425 --> 49:24.294
Oh, this is
a nonsmoking section.

49:24.427 --> 49:25.662
Okay, well,
I don't want to do anything

49:25.795 --> 49:27.297
that's not the normal routine.

49:27.430 --> 49:29.232
-You can smoke at the bar.
-No, that's fine.

49:29.332 --> 49:30.500
There are plenty of seats
at the bar if you want...

49:30.633 --> 49:33.670
No, I don't want to go
to the bar. Thank you.

49:33.803 --> 49:35.838
-Enjoy.
-Thank you.

49:35.972 --> 49:38.007
(piano music plays quietly)

49:49.186 --> 49:51.254
(sighs)

50:14.211 --> 50:15.678
Hi.

50:15.845 --> 50:17.814
Hi, Monica.

50:17.947 --> 50:19.982
-(sighs)
-It's her.

50:21.351 --> 50:23.186
LINDA:
Listen.

50:23.353 --> 50:25.788
I have been thinking
about you nonstop.

50:25.888 --> 50:28.024
I know I've been out of touch.

50:28.191 --> 50:31.494
Things feel so weird, and our
last conversation was so...

50:31.628 --> 50:33.330
I'm sorry.
I've-I've been a wreck.

50:33.463 --> 50:34.631
Me too.

50:34.731 --> 50:36.666
Why have you been a wreck?

50:36.799 --> 50:40.237
MONICA:
Because I'm in a nightmare.

50:40.370 --> 50:42.872
I feel like I'm going crazy,
like actual DSM crazy.

50:43.005 --> 50:44.507
I don't understand
what's happening or why.

50:44.641 --> 50:45.908
What do you...
what do you mean?

50:46.042 --> 50:47.810
What do you mean,
"What do I mean?"

50:47.910 --> 50:51.214
I feel an overwhelming sense of
dread every minute of every day,

50:51.348 --> 50:53.150
and honestly,
you're not helping with that.

50:53.250 --> 50:55.985
-I know. I know.
-You dropped off the face
of the earth, Linda.

50:56.085 --> 50:58.255
You were gonna go talk
to a lawyer, right?

50:58.388 --> 51:00.423
-Did that happen?
-Uh, I did,

51:00.557 --> 51:04.194
but, uh, it's-it's all still
very much up in the air.

51:04.327 --> 51:05.728
-Well, what does that mean?
-Thank you.

51:05.895 --> 51:07.730
Mm. Can I get you ladies
anything?

51:07.897 --> 51:09.566
No, nothing.
No, no.

51:09.699 --> 51:12.369
-I'd love some coffee, please.
-Mm-hmm.

51:19.776 --> 51:21.678
I need to know
what you're thinking

51:21.778 --> 51:23.546
about your affidavit.

51:23.680 --> 51:26.849
Are you still planning to lie?

51:26.949 --> 51:29.419
I already signed it.

51:29.552 --> 51:31.888
Nice.

51:32.021 --> 51:34.191
MONICA:
My thing with him was personal

51:34.291 --> 51:37.227
and private, and it has
absolutely nothing to do

51:37.360 --> 51:40.096
with Paula Jones, and I...
I really thought about it.

51:40.230 --> 51:42.799
And maybe if this were a...
a serious lawsuit,

51:42.932 --> 51:45.268
I would feel differently,
but I...

51:45.402 --> 51:48.104
I'm not helping
with a publicity stunt.

51:48.238 --> 51:50.072
I'm just... I'm not, okay?
And I think

51:50.207 --> 51:52.209
-you would feel the same way
if you would just...
-Okay.

51:52.309 --> 51:54.211
I-I'm not even concerned
with her.

51:54.311 --> 51:55.945
I'm concerned with us.

51:56.078 --> 51:57.947
Me too.

51:58.080 --> 51:59.916
Linda, I have to say,

52:00.049 --> 52:02.419
I've turned this over
in my mind a million times,

52:02.552 --> 52:04.454
and if the shoe were
on the other foot,

52:04.587 --> 52:05.922
I would keep your secret.

52:06.055 --> 52:08.325
I know I would do that for you.

52:14.130 --> 52:16.098
So...

52:16.233 --> 52:18.735
you've lied under oath,

52:18.835 --> 52:22.104
and you're asking me
to do the same.

52:25.408 --> 52:27.677
-Why are you saying it
like that?
-What do you mean?

52:27.810 --> 52:29.979
In legalese or whatever.

52:30.112 --> 52:31.981
Oh. Fuck.

52:32.114 --> 52:33.616
-LINDA: I don't know, Monica.
-Shh.

52:33.750 --> 52:34.984
I'm-I'm frightened.

52:35.117 --> 52:37.287
Okay.
I just... I think...

52:37.420 --> 52:39.589
(static crackling)

52:39.689 --> 52:41.924
-JACKIE: What's happening?
-The mic fell down.

52:42.024 --> 52:43.526
-Down where?!
-Probably in her blouse.

52:43.660 --> 52:45.262
-Go. Go, go.
-Go. Go.

52:45.362 --> 52:47.364
And tell her
to bring up Vernon Jordan!

52:47.497 --> 52:50.500
-What's going on?
-I'm just itchy. Go ahead.

52:50.633 --> 52:51.968
I think you're making this
into something that it's not.

52:52.101 --> 52:53.370
All you have to do, if they ask,

52:53.503 --> 52:54.937
is say, "I don't remember.

52:55.037 --> 52:56.606
I don't recall..."
Okay, what's-what's happening?

52:56.706 --> 52:59.776
I just... I'm gonna go
to the bathroom.

52:59.876 --> 53:01.711
I'll be right back.
(sighs)

53:03.813 --> 53:05.848
(panting)

53:15.358 --> 53:17.860
Ah, I got it.

53:18.027 --> 53:19.962
Get her to talk
about Vernon Jordan.

53:20.062 --> 53:21.964
Jesus Christ. Your one job
was to properly clip.

53:22.064 --> 53:23.966
-Okay, just breathe.
-Oh, shut up.

53:24.066 --> 53:26.135
I know how to breathe.
Sorry.

53:33.643 --> 53:35.678
The target is going through
the asset's purse.

53:36.846 --> 53:38.315
Hello.

53:38.415 --> 53:40.550
(whispering):
Hello. Is someone listening?

53:45.388 --> 53:46.756
(glass clinks)

53:46.889 --> 53:48.925
(coughing)

53:50.026 --> 53:52.662
(quietly): God.
Stop being paranoid, Monica.

53:52.762 --> 53:54.331
(sighs)

53:54.431 --> 53:57.334
-(glass clinking)
-(quietly): Shit. Fuck.

54:04.774 --> 54:07.109
Ah.
(sighs)

54:08.711 --> 54:10.112
You okay?

54:10.246 --> 54:12.114
Mm. Yeah.

54:12.248 --> 54:13.249
-Sorry. I...
-We're back! We're back!

54:13.416 --> 54:14.951
-We're back! We're back!
-Listen.

54:16.218 --> 54:17.854
(sighs)

54:17.954 --> 54:21.090
I know this might sound insane,

54:21.257 --> 54:24.427
but this whole situation,
I think, in a way--

54:24.561 --> 54:27.063
it might be easier for you
than it is for me.

54:27.196 --> 54:30.867
I'm a peon.
I don't have powerful friends.

54:30.967 --> 54:33.770
I have nobody.

54:33.936 --> 54:36.305
But you, I mean...
(laughs)

54:36.439 --> 54:41.411
You've got huge heavy hitters
in your back pocket.

54:41.544 --> 54:42.979
You're protected.

54:43.112 --> 54:44.781
What actual protection
do you think I have?

54:44.947 --> 54:46.749
I am not protected at all.

54:46.883 --> 54:49.419
Vernon Jordan got you a big job,
didn't he?

54:49.552 --> 54:50.553
Yes.

54:50.653 --> 54:51.954
Yes! Yes!

54:52.088 --> 54:53.456
LINDA:
You've got the president

54:53.590 --> 54:55.157
of the United States
looking out for you.

54:55.291 --> 54:56.593
MONICA:
Right, and if this gets out,

54:56.726 --> 54:57.727
he will hate me forever.

54:57.827 --> 55:00.096
(laughing):
Jesus, Monica.

55:00.229 --> 55:03.099
It just always comes back
to what's best for him.

55:03.232 --> 55:05.134
No, Linda.
It's me.

55:05.267 --> 55:07.003
This is for me.

55:07.136 --> 55:09.739
And all you have to do is say

55:09.839 --> 55:11.741
that you've never seen the
president behave inappropriately

55:11.841 --> 55:15.311
with anyone,
because that is 100% the truth.

55:19.649 --> 55:21.484
-I need to think about it.
-You keep saying that.

55:21.651 --> 55:22.819
-You have thought about it.
-I know.

55:22.985 --> 55:24.621
Linda, please.

55:24.754 --> 55:27.156
Please. This is my real life
we're talking about,

55:27.323 --> 55:29.826
and I'm scared.

55:29.959 --> 55:33.262
(sighs) All I need is for you
to say that you just won't

55:33.362 --> 55:35.498
tell them about me.
Please?

55:35.632 --> 55:37.199
Please.

55:41.438 --> 55:43.673
It's a big decision.
Let me sleep on it.

55:43.806 --> 55:46.208
I don't understand why
you can't just promise me that.

55:46.342 --> 55:48.645
You're asking a lot.

55:48.778 --> 55:51.313
I need the night, okay?

55:57.687 --> 56:00.356
(laughs softly)

56:04.627 --> 56:06.863
-He's put you through so much.
-(sighs)

56:07.029 --> 56:09.231
All I want is
for you to be free of it.

56:09.365 --> 56:11.200
-I hope you know that.
-I...

56:11.333 --> 56:14.036
-I don't know.
-I'll call you tomorrow,
I promise.

56:25.414 --> 56:27.149
(shutter clicking)
